author: er433
description: '### Soon to be deprecated: `Tezos.amount`, `Tezos.balance`, `Tezos.now`,
  `Tezos.sender`, `Tezos.source`, `Tezos.level`, `Tezos.self_address`, `Tezos.chain_id`,
  `Tezos.total_voting_power`.\n\nThese should be replaced by their \"thunked\" counterpart,
  which are prefixed with `get_`. E.g. `Tezos.balance : unit -> tez`.'
